    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People or corporate bodies who design the plan and features of gardens, which are open space where flowers, shrubs, trees, vegetables, or fruits are grown. Garden designers may be amateurs or professionals. For those who practice the branch of architecture dealing with the design of the scenic environment, including plants and surrounding roads and structures, use "landscape architects."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
